  ('The distance from point P=(x₁,y₁,z₁) to plane Ax+By+Cz=D is ___.',['|AP₁|','√(A²+B²+C²)','|Ax₁+By₁+Cz₁|','|Ax₁+By₁+Cz₁−D|/√(A²+B²+C²) — a formula analogous to the 2D point-to-line distance'],3),
  ('Two lines in 3D can be ___.',['only parallel or intersecting','always coplanar','always intersecting','parallel, intersecting, or skew (non-parallel, non-intersecting lines that do not lie in the same plane)'],3),
