  ('An oral culminating in Grade 12 English demonstrates ___.',['only public speaking skill','only the ability to memorise','only knowledge of plot','the integration of all your analytical learning: the ability to think aloud, respond to texts in real time, construct an argument under pressure, and communicate sophisticated ideas to an audience'],3),
